subtitle: notes on the seminar given by Prof. Dr. C.G. Jung, Zurich, Winter 1935
title: Psychological analysis of Nietzche's Zarathustra

notes.value:
Ress, L.  Jung, p. 213
Mimeographed transcript of the seminar.
"This report is strictly for the use of members of the seminar"--Vol. 3, prelim. leaf [3]
According to Ress, this is the undated 2nd ed., all volumes of which are typed with uniform (single-line) spacing. The 1st ed., 1934-1939, was typed with double spacing in v. 1-3 and single spacing in the others.
An index, by Mary Briner, was issued in 1942. Cf. Ress.
